snippet.title: World of Warcraft Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the official cinematic trailer for World of Warcraft, which marked the launch of the game that took the world by storm.

Learn more about the story of World of Warcraft here:
http://battle.net/wow/game/the-story-of-warcraft/chapter6
